defects // Lancet. 1996; 248: 1037-1038.<br/>24. Lucas A. A programming by early nutrition in man. In: Bock GR; Whelan J (eds): The childhood environment and adult disease. Ciba Foundation Symposium 156.<br/>25. Shaw G.M., Lammer E.J., Wasserman C.R. et al. Risks of orofacial clefts in children born to women using multivitamins containing folic acid periconceptionally // Lancet. 1995, : 393-396. <br/>26. Shrimpton D.H. Nutritional implications of micronutrients interactions. // Chemist and Druggist. 2004; 15: 38-41.</p>
